<h2><strong><a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/audio-equipment-sound-rentals">Audio Equipment Rentals</a></strong></h2>
We supply an array of audio for meetings, presentations, press conferences, and professional events of all sizes. Our selection of speakers, PA systems, microphones, press boxes and digital audio recorders are designed to be customizable for any purpose, with countless possible configurations.
<h2><strong><a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/projector-rentals">Projector Rentals</a></strong></h2>
Hook our standard meeting projector up to your laptop or DVD player to show a movie or PowerPoint presentation in mere seconds. Connect it to your Nintendo Wii or Xbox for large-scale multiplayer competition at your next teambuilding event. Our large-venue projectors offer scale and flexibility that conventional video technology can't accommodate. How else could you make a display the size of a three-story building with a 50-foot diagonal?
<h2><strong><a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/professional-video-camera-rental">Video Camera Rentals</a></strong></h2>
Whether you need a Panasonic DVX or Canon GL2 to produce a professional video, or an easy-to-use digital DVD camera to play your recording back immediately, we can help. All of our camcorder rentals include professional tripods, additional batteries and tapes, and options such as mounted lights and shotgun mics. We offer daily and weekly video camera rentals, online ordering and delivery right to your meeting venue, office or other location.
<h2><strong><a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/flat-screen-monitor-rentals">Video DisplayÂ Rentals</a></strong></h2>
We offer the latest in audio/visual technology, whether a la carte or as part of a full audio visual package for your event. Outfit our plasmas with speakers and professional floor stands, connect our LCD monitor to your computer for a dazzling large display, or let your customers or guests interact with the computer via touchscreen technology (up to 46" diagonal). We can set up kiosks for video games, computer software (keyboard or touchscreen), or looping video of your choice.
